description:
Mô Tả Công Việc


              * Working place: Duong Xa, Gia Lam, Ha Noi (Company provides bus to pick up staff from center of Hanoi)

              * Job Description:

              - Design and develop ceramic products with the complete structure, and finish the 2D & 3D drawing and mold design. Make sure the product match the requested standards and can be produced by a normal process. At the same time, make sure the product following the designer's request.

              - Have to communicate and discuss with the modeler team and component engineer, defeat the problem that would happen.

              - Ensuring the completion of engineering documentation to support product introductions and/or revisions.

              - Other duties assigned by Manager.

              * Benefits

              - Working in a multicultural and excellent environment with attractive benefit that promotes creative thinking and intellectual grow;

              - Healthcare Insurance BaoViet/ Aon

              - Enjoy an average of 03 Saturday and 04 Sunday off per month;

              - Enjoy a favorable bonus scheme includes fixed bonus, incentive bonus and profit bonus;

              - Fair and transparent change for promotion based on your own performance;

              - Birthday allowance;

              - Company provides bus to pick up staff from center of Hanoi


              Xem toàn bộ Mô Tả Công Việc

requirement:
Yêu Cầu Công Việc


              - Bachelor degree or higher in mechanical or industrial design

              - Able to use proficiently AutoCAD software engineering & office software; have good command of 3D software such as ProE/CAM (must);

              - Experience for mold design in sanitary ware is preferable.

              - Good English skills and Communication skills (must);

              - Good manual practical ability

              - Work proactively, having teamwork spirit and nimble;

              - Able to commit to work for long-term.


